OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784715503
OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,7,FYoussef spoke to patients and staff at
OL,8,Fthe Wigan and Leigh Hospice.
OL,10,FA hospice in Makerfield - the
OL,11,Fconstituency of newly-appointed Prime
OL,12,FMinister Andy Burnham - is calling for
OL,13,Fhim to make fairer funding for
OL,14,Fhospices on of his top priorities.
OL,16,FWigan and Leigh Hospice has launched a
OL,17,Fcampaign inviting local people to
OL,18,Fshare their experiences of hospice
OL,19,Fcare and explain why their services
OL,20,Fmatter, at a time when hospices face
OL,21,Fgrowing financial pressures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
