OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,FFormer carer Jane Bourne, 57, was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with cancer of the
OL,8,Foesophagus in 2023, and went into the
OL,9,Fhospice in July 2026.
OL,11,FShe said: "The week before I came into
OL,12,Fthe hospice I'd given up. If I hadn't
OL,13,Fbeen given this lifeline I wouldn't be
OL,14,Fhere now.
OL,16,F"There was no fight left and a lot of
OL,17,Fit was down to pain and not being
OL,18,Flistened to. I wasn't me, I'd lost me.
OL,19,FThere was no Jane - I had no spark."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784715503
OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,FWith the help of medication and her
OL,7,Fnurse at the hospice, Jane is hoping
OL,8,Fto go home soon.
OL,10,FShe said: "The level of care I have
OL,11,Fhad here I would describe it as my
OL,12,Flittle paradise.
OL,14,F"Within three or four days i was up
OL,15,Fwalking about causing mischief
OL,16,Fnormally and couldn't believe myself
OL,17,Fthat I had gone from where I was to
OL,18,Fwhere I am now is amazing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
