PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784715503
OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,FAndy Burnham took part in the London
OL,7,FMarathon for the hospice in 2014 when
OL,8,Fhe was MP for Leigh.
OL,10,FCEO Jo Carby said donations from local
OL,11,Fpeople are the only way the hospice
OL,12,Fstays open, as they need to raise
OL,13,F#13,000 per day on top of NHS funding
OL,14,Fto cover their costs.
OL,16,FShe said: "Our Wigan borough community
OL,17,Fare so generous, but they have their
OL,18,Fown financial challenges, we're in a
OL,19,Fcost of living crisis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784715503
OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,F"It isn't fair and it isn't right that
OL,7,Four community should have to cover
OL,8,Fthis bill. Our NHS funding doesn't
OL,9,Fincrease year to year by sufficient
OL,10,Famounts, so we are asking our
OL,11,Fcommunity to fill that gap.
OL,13,F"If it wasn't for them, we simply
OL,14,Fwouldn't be here."
OL,16,FMs Carby said the hospice will have to
OL,17,Fcut back on services and staff if they
OL,18,Fdon't receive more funding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784715503
OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,F"The situation in Wigan and Leigh
OL,7,FHospice is mirrored across the
OL,8,Fcountry. Most hospices are struggling
OL,9,Fbecause the financial model by which
OL,10,Fwe're funded isn't fit for purpose.
OL,12,F"Some hospices will be struggling more
OL,13,Fthan others - we see hospices having
OL,14,Fto reduce services and make staff
OL,15,Fredundant pretty much every month.
OL,17,F"It's happening all the time, so we're
OL,18,Fall in this crisis of how we ensure
OL,19,Fthat we continue to provide the
OL,20,Fservices that we know our community
OL,21,Fneeds."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
