OL,3,CMakerfield charity says Burnham should
OL,4,Cmake hospice funding top priority as PM
OL,6,FJane is hoping the hospice's 'Dear PM'
OL,7,Fcampaign will push the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fto allocate more funding to palliative
OL,9,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
